imdb.plot outline: A story of the almost impossible love between Luís Miguel and Mara, set in Lisbon and Luanda. The relationship of Luís and Mara will be affected with the conspiracies and secrets of their friends and family, either in Portugal or Angola, as the lives of each character is changed by those same conspiracies and secrets.
imdb.title: A Única Mulher
plot: A story of the almost impossible love between Luís Miguel and Mara, set in Lisbon and Luanda. The relationship of Luís and Mara will be affected with the conspiracies and secrets of their friends and family, either in Portugal or Angola, as the lives of each character is changed by those same conspiracies and secrets.
synopsis:
The collapse of a large national bank triggers the (re) encounter of two realities. And the conflict between two families.
  
Luis Miguel is a young engineer who seeks a career in Angola. Back, it leaves a traditional and conservative family, affected by the crisis. His father owns a national construction company at risk of bankruptcy, and his mother waiting out rich from a broken marriage.
  
In Angola, Luís Miguel knows Mara, a nurse who saves him from certain death. The girl's father is an Angolan businessman with important investments in Portugal and also the main customer of construction. He has in hand the fate of the company but has great resentment against the Portuguese that during the colonial war, murdered his father. The legacy of this past and the interests of this turn what would be a business dispute in the clash of two worlds.
  
But nothing survives the revenge of a woman. Luena is the daughter of returnees who have lost everything they had, with the independence of Angola. She wants to retrieve the family heritage, above all. Even itself ...
